Package: hotteR
Type: Package
Title: Hottest 100 Countdown and Triple J Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Trent Henderson
Maintainer: Trent Henderson <trent.henderson1@outlook.com>
Description: Automates extraction of @triplejplays data and produces Hottest 100 Countdown analysis.
             Some functions in the package access the Twitter API and thus require appropriate
             credentials to be available in the R Environment prior to running. The 'twitteR'
             package provides a useful setup_twitter_oauth() function for this.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr, 
    magrittr,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    stringr,
    ggpubr,
    janitor,
    rtweet,
    rvest,
    XML
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
